# 🎫 Help Desk Ticket

## Issue

User cannot remotely connect to the Linux server.

### Investigation

Checked SSH service status.

Result:

ssh.service not found.

### Root Cause

OpenSSH Server was not installed.

### Resolution

Installed OpenSSH Server.

Verified SSH service is active and enabled.

Issue resolved.

